overview:
Established in the year 2011, we, “Highway Screws & Fasteners”, are an eminent firm, which is engaged in importing, supplying and trading a wide assembly of Screws and Fasteners. Under this range, we offer Industrial Hex Self Drilling Screws, Oval Wafer Truss Head Self Drilling Screws, Pan Phillips Head Self Drilling Zinc Plated Screws, Oval Wafer Truss Head Self Tapping Black Phosphates Screws, Hardened Drywall Screws, CSK Phillips Head Self Drilling Screws, Anchor Fasteners, Metal Nuts, Metal Bolts and Metal Washers.

Our Products: Self Drilling Screws Oval Wafer Truss Head Drywall Screws Self Drilling Screws CSK Phillips Head

Our Manpower: We have been able to come up with a hard working team of able personnel, which aids us in offering an unmatched range of Screws and Fasteners. The personnel hired by us are selected via stringent measures, in order to assure of their capabilities and professional work zone.

Vendor Base: We always ensure to source the offered range of Screws and Fasteners from the authentic vendors of the market. These vendors are chosen on the basis of different factors such as raw material used, market stature and infrastructure. Along with this, vendors ensure to design the offered range utilizing premium grade raw material and modern machinery.

Warehouse: We are able to construct a commodious warehousing department, which aids us effectively in storing a vast range of Screws and Fasteners. The facility is suitably temperature controlled so as to keep the sourced range away from the adverse elements.
